'''萌生'''是[[植物|植物]]适应环境干扰的一种更新策略<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bond |first1=William J. |last2=Midgley |first2=Jeremy J. |title=The Evolutionary Ecology of Sprouting in Woody Plants |journal=International Journal of Plant Sciences |date=2003-05 |volume=164 |issue=S3 |pages=S103–S114 |doi=10.1086/374191}}</ref>。一些植物从被火烧、干旱或被砍伐的[[根|根]]部、树干基部的[[木质瘤|木质瘤]]等产生新的枝苗，从而形成多茎干植株<ref>{{cite journal |author1=闫恩荣 |coauthors=王希华, 施家月, 王希波, 王良衍 |title=木本植物萌枝生态学研究进展 |journal=应用生态学报 |date=2005 |volume=16 |issue=12 |pages=2459-2464 |url=http://www.cjae.net/CN/abstract/abstract7594.shtml}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Paula |first1=S. |last2=Pausas |first2=J. G. |title=Leaf traits and resprouting ability in the Mediterranean basin |journal=Functional Ecology |date=2006-12 |volume=20 |issue=6 |pages=941–947 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2435.2006.01185.x}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Paula |first1=S. |last2=Arianoutsou |first2=M. |last3=Kazanis |first3=D. |last4=Tavsanoglu |first4=Ç |last5=Lloret |first5=F. |last6=Buhk |first6=C. |last7=Ojeda |first7=F. |last8=Luna |first8=B. |last9=Moreno |first9=J. M. |last10=Rodrigo |first10=A. |last11=Espelta |first11=J. M. |last12=Palacio |first12=S. |last13=Fernández-Santos |first13=B. |last14=Fernandes |first14=P. M. |last15=Pausas |first15=J. G. |title=Fire-related traits for plant species of the Mediterranean Basin: Ecological Archives E090-094 |journal=Ecology |date=2009-05 |volume=90 |issue=5 |pages=1420–1420 |doi=10.1890/08-1309.1}}</ref>。这也是[[森林管理|森林管理]]的一种传统方式。萌生出的茎干数量常作为萌生能力的表征指标<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Xiulian |first1=Chi |last2=Qinggang |first2=Wang |last3=Qiang |first3=Guo |last4=Xian |first4=Yang |last5=Zhiyao |first5=Tang |title=Sprouting characteristics of communities during succession in an evergreen broad-leaved forest on Gutian Mountain, East China |journal=Biodiversity Science |date=2019-01-20 |volume=27 |issue=1 |pages=24 |doi=10.17520/biods.2018222}}</ref>。

